data.description: Large Mt Airy Duplex in a great location just block off the main thoroughfare of Germantown Ave, with tons of shopping and restaurants as well as easy access to anywhere else in the city, also within walking distance from the popular Weaver's Way Co-op, is just a stone's throw away. Great location if want to commute via mass transit. Or if you're not looking to go that far, the main commercial corridor of Germantown Ave has all you'll need! The area is packed to the brim with local history and museums with multiple historical sites in neighboring Germantown within a mile of the property. Into nature?  The property is flanked by parks, including the famous Wissahickon Valley Park with loads to do! The property itself is an immense corner property with a well-maintained brick facade, the downstairs unit opens up to a beautifully renovated 2 bedroom, 1 bath unit with all new appliances, bells & whistles. The second-floor unit, also 2 bedrooms and one bathroom apartment is in move-in ready condition.  The property is a great value-add opportunity for an experienced investor to put a little work in and get a lot out or a great opportunity for a buyer to live in one unit and rent out the other to offset the mortgage!
